import { Button, Card, CardActionArea, CardActions, CardContent, CardMedia, Typography } from '@mui/material';
import React from 'react'

export const Feed = () => {
  return (

    <Card sx={{ maxWidth: 400 , marginTop:"50px",marginLeft:"100px",marginRight:"10px"}}>
      <CardActionArea>
        <CardMedia
          component="img"
          height="200"
          image="https://cdn.dsmcdn.com/ty864/pimWidgetApi/mobile_20230504173320_2316859ElektronikMobile202305042001.jpg"
          alt="teknosa"
        />
        <CardContent>
          <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div">
            teknosa
          </Typography>

        </CardContent>
      </CardActionArea>
      <CardActions>
        <Button
        size='small'
        color='inherit'
         >
          alışverişe başla
        </Button>
      </CardActions>
    </Card>
  );
}
